@startuml Serverless To-Do API Architecture

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title Serverless To-Do API Architecture

actor User as "User"
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Lambda Function" as Lambda
database "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB

User -> APIGW: HTTP Request (GET/POST/DELETE)
APIGW -> Lambda: Invoke Function
Lambda -> DynamoDB: Query/Scan/Write Operations
DynamoDB -> Lambda: Return Data
Lambda -> APIGW: HTTP Response
APIGW -> User: JSON Response

note right of APIGW
  RESTful API Endpoints:
  - GET /tasks (list all tasks)
  - POST /tasks (create task)
  - DELETE /tasks/{id} (delete task)
end note

note right of Lambda
  Python Lambda Function:
  - Business logic
  - Data validation
  - DynamoDB operations
end note

note right of DynamoDB
  NoSQL Database:
  - Task items storage
  - Auto-scaling
  - Pay-per-request pricing
end note

@enduml
